pg</Url><Width>480</Width><Height>261</Height><Bytes>22800</Bytes><Caption>2631759-Ferrer-Janeiro-Hotel-Mallorca-Island-Guest-Room-2</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1116/32/08/18/2631759-Ferrer-Janeiro-Hotel-Mallorca-Island-Guest-Room-2thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>128</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2725</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Located in the zone of  son baulo, one of the most peaceful parts of ca´n picafort. only 80 m away from its beach of fine sand and transparent waters. it features a lifeguard and rescue service in summertime, is next to a natural park. the hotel is just a short distance away from the nautical port and shopping area. &lt;br&gt;Enjoy sun, sea and sand on this cheerful Mallorcan resort with the option of cooling off in the Mediterranean, just metres away, or in this hotels great outdoor pool. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Wake up to stunning weather that Mallorca enjoys for most of the year and gaze at the gorgeous views from your balcony. Take the short stroll down to the beach where you will find white sands, turquoise waters and safe swimming. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Enjoy a hearty, buffet breakfast in the air-conditioned restaurant or in the pleasant, outdoor seating area next to the pool. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;After a session in the Janeiros fitness centre, unwind in the sauna and Turkish baths. Why not treat yourself to a relaxing massage. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There is plenty to keep you outdoor and active this holiday with horse riding and diving excursions to explore Mallorca Island.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>1. Take the MA19 towards Palma for 4.2 km. &lt;br&gt;2. Take Exit 3 - Andratx, Port d'Alcudia and follow motorway for 2.6 km. &lt;br&gt;3. Take Exit 3 - Inca, Port d'Alcudia, Son Castelló and follow motorway for 26.3 km. &lt;br&gt;4. Take Exit 27 - Inca, Sineu, Lluc, Llubí, Hospital and follow the signs to Llubí or Santa Margalida. &lt;br&gt;5. Drive through Llubí. &lt;br&gt;6. Drive through Santa Margalida towards Ca'n Picafort. &lt;br&gt;7. After 3.5 km. turn right towards Ca'n Picafort. &lt;br&gt;8. Follow road for 3.5 km. &lt;br&gt;9. At the Ca'n Picafort access roundabout continue straight ahead. &lt;br&gt;10. Turn right on Av. Diagonal. &lt;br&gt;11. At the end of the road you will find first Hotel Ferrer Janeiro.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>STANDARD - ROOM - the ferrer janeiro disposes of 211 rooms distributed in 5 floors, in a one-storey building right in the neighbourhood of the hotel. all rooms are equipped with air-conditioning / heating, complete bathroom, satellite tv, direct outward dialling phone, safety deposit box and balcony. daily cannier and accurate cleaning service&lt;br&gt;double rooms avalable with side sea view.some of the single rooms dont have a balcony. Non-smoker rooms are available.childrens cot free.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Sauna</Code><Text>Sauna</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Whirlpool</Code><Text>Whirlpool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money exchange</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CloakRoom</Code><Text>Cloak Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></A